<section class="guarantee-area-about">
<div class="container">
  <div class="row justify-content-center text-center">
    <div class="col-md-12">
      <!-- <h2 class="h2-common color-yellow mb-19">
        WE TRULY CARE. THEY DON'T!
      </h2> -->
      <h1 class="h1-common">OUR SEAMLESS GUARANTEE</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col">
      <ol class="list-items">
        <li>
          <span>Zero Upfront Fees - </span>Most funders will charge as
          much as a 10% origination fee. At Seamless, we've worked with
          our funders to ensure there are never any fees to get funded.
          Ever.
        </li>
        <li>
          <span>Zero Processing Fees - </span> If your business takes
          credit cards, we can help you virtually eliminate your credit
          fees with Seamless Zero.
        </li>
        <li>
          <span>Zero Hassles - </span>Don't worry about hurting your
          credit, forget the endless calls and aggressive brokers. With
          Seamless, you will fill out one application and we will generate
          offers from our network of funding partners. No salespeople, no
          hard credit pulls, no hassles.
        </li>
        <li>
          <span>Zero Balance Promise - </span> As business owners, we
          understand that a little help can go a long way. To stand by our
          commitment to the business owner we will randomly zero out the
          balance of one of our Seamless VIPs accounts each and every
          month! This is our way of saying Thank You for doing business
          with us.
        </li>
      </ol>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <div class="mt-50">
        <h1 class="h1-common">our mission</h1>
        <p class="p-common mb-0">
          To empower the small business to fund their future by
          demonstrating a perposeful commitment to guiding our customers
          with optionality, integrity, and radical transparency.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="col-md-6">
      <div class="mt-50">
        <h1 class="h1-common">values</h1>
        <p class="p-common mb-0">
          Maniacal focus on our customer, Radical transparency, Passion
          for our product, Have fun
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</section>

<section class="information-area-about">
<div class="container">
  <div class="row align-items-center">
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <div class="text-wrap">
        <h1 class="h1-common mb-2">More Questions?</h1>
        <p class="p-common mb-0">Let our Funding Concierge reach out.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-6">
      <div class="right-div">
        <form
          class="row row-cols-lg-auto g-3 width-480 align-items-center needs-validation"
          novalidate
        >
          <div class="col-6 col-margin">
            <input
              type="text"
              class="form-control input-area"
              id="firstNameInfo"
              placeholder="First Name*"
              required
            />
            <div class="invalid-feedback">can't be blank</div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-6 col-margin">
            <input
              type="text"
              class="form-control input-area"
              id="lastNameInfo"
              placeholder="Last Name*"
              required
            />
            <div class="invalid-feedback">can't be blank</div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-6 col-margin">
            <input
              type="text"
              class="form-control input-area"
              id="companyInfo"
              placeholder="Company*"
              required
            />
            <div class="invalid-feedback">can't be blank</div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-6 col-margin">
            <input
              type="text"
              class="form-control input-area"
              id="phoneInfo"
              placeholder="Phone Number*"
              required
            />
            <div class="invalid-feedback">can't be blank</div>
          </div>

          <div class="col-12 col-margin">
            <input
              type="text"
              class="form-control input-area"
              id="emailInfo"
              placeholder="Email*"
              required
            />
            <div class="invalid-feedback">can't be blank</div>
          </div>
          <div class="col-12">
            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-yellow color-purple">
              <a href="#">GET IN TOUCH</a>
            </button>
          </div>
        </form>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
</section>
